    "\n",
    "# 🟢 Solution: Implement ReLU\n",
    "\n",
    "Reference solution for the ReLU activation function.\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\text{ReLU}(x) = \\max(0, x)$$"
   ],
   "outputs": []
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ✅ SOLUTION\n",
    "\n",
    "def relu(x: torch.Tensor) -> torch.Tensor:\n",
    "    return x * (x > 0).float()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Verify\n",
    "x = torch.tensor([-2., -1., 0., 1., 2.])\n",
    "print(\"Input: \", x)\n",
    "print(\"Output:\", relu(x))"
   ]
  },
